    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244740/extras/f110004ee85416670c1aa5de8ee7c0a5.avif?t=1731419575\" width=590 height=629 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >老板，回来啦！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拯救了世界之后，是不是在想后来又发生什么了？尘埃落定之后，大家在阿斯忒里亚过得怎么样？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《魔饮心语》那些事情发生了一年半之后，年轻的侦探梅琳娜发现了一个神秘装置，可是不小心弄坏了，把困在里面混乱的精魂放了出来。她和朋友必须尽快修好这台古代装置，抓回精魂，防止一场原始风暴造成惨重的破坏。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >这位是奥利安达·维里菲纳！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >下面有请菲薄甘于忍让的哥哥、灰烬林地长期加班的游侠奥利安达。他并不想现身什么冒险剧情，只是命运的想法与他不同……我们就在寻路者酒馆以最大的热情好好招待他吧！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244740/extras/7ebfb30e99c036583b2039d6dde99b39.poster.avif?t=1731419575\" width=500 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244740/extras/7ebfb30e99c036583b2039d6dde99b39.webm?t=1731419575\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244740/extras/7ebfb30e99c036583b2039d6dde99b39.mp4?t=1731419575\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >发现新的配方和魔药！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的故事仿佛微风拂面！调一杯微微冒泡的“嘶嘶海洋”，穿过滔天的波峰浪谷之间，加一份荧光水藻，让你的魔饮发出光来！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244740/extras/96f1619aeb785dc0ace994ee7da636a8.avif?t=1731419575\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3244740/extras_big/96f1619aeb785dc0ace994ee7da636a8.avif?t=1731419575 width=800 height=406 /></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >多个结局</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《风暴骤起》将给第一周目添加大约三个小时的新剧情，另外包含了四种结局和三项任务！</p>",
